import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    sns.set(style="whitegrid")
    chart = sns.countplot(x="Airport_Name", data=data, order=data['Airport_Name'].value_counts().index)
    chart.set_xticklabels(chart.get_xticklabels(), rotation=90, horizontalalignment='right')
    chart.set_xlabel('Airport Name')
    chart.set_ylabel('Number of Bird Strikes')
    chart.axhline(y=data['Airport_Name'].value_counts().max(), color='r', linestyle='--', label='Max: {:.2f}'.format(data['Airport_Name'].value_counts().max()))
    chart.legend()
    plt.title('What is the distribution of bird strikes by airport?', wrap=True)
    return plt

chart = plot(data)
```

import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    plt.figure(figsize=(12, 6))
    ax = sns.countplot(x='Aircraft_Make_Model', data=data, order=data['Aircraft_Make_Model'].value_counts().iloc[:10].index, palette='Blues_d')
    ax.set(xlabel='Aircraft Make and Model', ylabel='Count')
    ax.set_xticklabels(ax.get_xticklabels(), rotation=45, ha='right')
    ax.axhline(y=data['Aircraft_Make_Model'].value_counts().iloc[0], color='r', linestyle='--', label='Most Common Aircraft Make and Model: {:.2f}'.format(data['Aircraft_Make_Model'].value_counts().iloc[0]))
    plt.legend()
    return plt

chart = plot(data)
```

import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data = data.dropna(subset=['Phase_of_flight'])
    phase_of_flight_counts = data['Phase_of_flight'].value_counts()
    plt.pie(phase_of_flight_counts, labels=phase_of_flight_counts.index, autopct='%1.1f%%')
    plt.title('What is the distribution of bird strikes by phase of flight?')
    return plt

chart = plot(data)
```
